com.aionemu.gameserver.ai.desires
Interface Desire

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Desire>
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractDesire, AggressionDesire, AttackDesire, MoveToHomeDesire, MoveToTargetDesire, RestoreHealthDesire, ServantAi.ServantSkillUseDesire, SkillUseDesire, TrapAi.TrapExplodeDesire, WalkDesire
public interface Desire
extends java.lang.Comparable<Desire>

This interface represents basic desire functions.
Each desire should implement handleDesire(com.aionemu.gameserver.ai.AI) method with default behaviour.
AI can override com.aionemu.gameserver.ai.AI#handleDesire(Desire) to implement custom behaviour of desire.

Author:
SoulKeeper
See Also:
AI, com.aionemu.gameserver.ai.AI#handleDesire(Desire), AbstractDesire

increaseDesirePower

void increaseDesirePower(int desirePower)
Adds desire power to this desire, this call is synchronized.

WARNING!!! Changing desire power after adding it to queue will not affect it's position, you have to call DesireQueue.addDesire(Desire) passing this instance as argument

Parameters:
